    "sidebarcontentbottom": "[quote]What happens when I get caught?! I never get caught! Otherwise I wouldn't be here, would I? But how sweet of you to worry about me, dear. Always remember this: one should always have at least two backup plans in case things go south. One is an escape, and the other is having the means to fend of whoever wants to hurt you.|A laughing Ashish Ludak[/quote]",
